    question: "Do callers reply to the text?",
    answer: "Frequently — especially homeowners with a clear project in mind. Typical replies include the metalwork type, approximate dimensions, material preference, design style, and postcode. These descriptive replies arrive in your lead dashboard before you return the call, allowing you to discuss design options with informed preparation."
